- [x] Database (filesystem)
- [ ] SSL, Authorization & Authentication, Rate Limiting, Input Validation, permission and roles
- [ ] Database (NoSQL)
- [ ] Database (SQL)
- [ ] Database (GraphQL)
- [ ] Caching and Perf
- [ ] Containerization and Microservices
- [ ] CI/CD
- [ ] Deployment